songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
I helped you for no dough
Trained you up to be cold
Bare copies bound to get sold
Ask anybody I know
It's not my fault got a youth club so
I wanna see everybody on the road
You're gonna fail that's what I got told
Ask anybody I know

[Verse]
I'm the best in the game it's a fact I know
I'm a producer, MC pro
I've got the title for two light builbs
Contenders gotta say no
'Cause they wanna be the one on the throne but no
Chat about grime you pick 50 songs I'll pick 50 songs and my style would show
I'm a don on the hype you're a don on the low
Yo, I'm too cold don't care if I'm old
I've been bad on the road since you changed flows
You and your manager know it's not a joke
I've got hits in my vault
And you can sit down like whoa
I know you're a champ but bro

[Chorus]
I helped you for no dough
Trained you up to be cold
Bare copies bound to get sold
Ask anybody I know
It's not my fault got a youth club so
I wanna see everybody on the road
You're gonna fail that's what I got told
Ask anybody I know
songs.title: Dizzee Rascal Diss (Instagram Freestyle)
